cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.HC 

The paper deals with the problem of face alignment, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper proposes a new evaluation metric and carries out a comparative analysis of recent face alignment methods, which involves training and testing machine learning models (cs.LG, cs.AI). The paper also extends the 300W database, which is related to multimedia (cs.MM), and provides suggestions for practical applications, which involves human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
